name: Bobby CHEN, petitioner, v. MAYOR AND CITY COUNCIL OF BALTIMORE, MARYLAND, et al.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties:
Bobby CHEN, petitioner,
v.
MAYOR AND CITY COUNCIL OF BALTIMORE, MARYLAND, et al.

opinions.text: Petitioner has not filed a brief on the merits within 45 days of the order granting the writ of certiorari, as required by Rule 25.1. Petitioner has neither requested an extension of time nor responded to correspondence directed to the mailing address provided under Rule 34.1(f). Additional efforts to contract petitioner have been unsuccessful. Writ of certiorari accordingly dismissed.
